## 12. What the system can be used for

The current architecture is especially suitable for application cases in which free AI answers alone are not sufficient.

These include, for example:

* structured consulting and analysis processes
* guided B2B diagnostics
* risk and compliance adjacent assessments
* AI supported domain reports
* hybrid processes of collection, processing, and textual condensation
* controlled user guidance in sensitive decision fields
* local or partially local systems with privacy and audit reference

The extensions already present show this direction very well: LinkedIn Postpilot, property insurance analysis, medical EU AI check, LCIS, and KSON are not random gimmicks, but evidence that the same platform can carry very different structured AI processes. 

