## 15. Summary

m-pathy is a **deterministic AI operating system** that brings together structured user guidance, controlled analysis, and optional real backend execution within one shared architecture. M13 provides the constitution, the system prompt makes it operational, route.ts conducts the runtime, engine.ts controls the state logic, registry.json addresses the modules, extensions define the domain programs, and the Execution Space brings the system into real processing. 

The result is not a chatbot and not a freely running agent, but a **governed AI platform** for controlled, traceable, and extensible AI processes.